formatDescription: QuadriSpace provide 3D Publishing and Documentation software. This entry currently covers each known QuadriSpace-specifc format, however it may be possible and necessary to separate different QuadriSpace formats into their own entries in the future.
provenanceCompoundName: Digital Preservation Department / The National Archives

internalSignatures.name: QuadriSpace Format
internalSignatures.note:
BOF: Ÿ.|N
With further research it may be possible to distinguish between different types of QuadriSpace formats. For now, known formats that conform to this signature pattern are:
.qsd - QuadriSpace Document Format
.qst - QuadriSpace Template
.qsm - QuadriSpace Model
.qsl - QuadriSpace Material
